modShortDescription: It is disturbing that cooked food and boiled water cause poisoning. This simple 7 Days to Die mod remove food poisoning from boiled water and cooked food.
modDescription:
It is a bit disturbing that cooked [food](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-food/) and boiled water cause poisoning. This simple 7 Days to Die mod remove food poisoning from boiled water and cooked food.

[Download](https://docs.google.com/uc?export=download&id=1KiSNSVP64_aSu-3knUcFW0I6UXfToWpN)

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/15770-food-poison-removal/).

**Credits:** UbberN00ber
